{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012YPk7egHfCvidAon3FzCsD","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t\\paragraph{1985 B--5 \\textnormal{[\\texttt{integral-evaluation}]}}\n2\tA reference asserts the following closed form. Determine whether the\n3\tassertion is correct.\n4\t\n5\t\\textbf{Claim.} For every positive integer $a$,\n6\t\\[\n7\t\\int_0^\\infty t^{-1/2}\\, e^{-a(t + t^{-1})}\\,dt \\;=\\;\n8\t\\sqrt{\\frac{\\pi}{a}}\\;e^{-2a}.\n9\t\\]\n10\t(In particular, for $a = 1985$ the value is $\\sqrt{\\pi/1985}\\,e^{-3970}$.)\n11\t\n12\tYou may assume that $\\int_{-\\infty}^\\infty e^{-x^2}\\,dx = \\sqrt{\\pi}$.\n13\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d12e7cbb-9aeb-4ed8-ad25-4641c17617c6","uuid":"ee997fa1-bf6e-45a9-8cac-d21858b20abb","timestamp":"2026-05-25T01:49:37.152Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/private/var/folders/pl/c57pb2_52t513h0r4dgr0ryc0000gn/T/fc_1985_B5__true__forced_textual__r5_zucl_hxb/1985_B5_true.tex","content":"\\paragraph{1985 B--5 \\textnormal{[\\texttt{integral-evaluation}]}}\nA reference asserts the following closed form. Determine whether the\nassertion is correct.\n\n\\textbf{Claim.} For every positive integer $a$,\n\\[\n\\int_0^\\infty t^{-1/2}\\, e^{-a(t + t^{-1})}\\,dt \\;=\\;\n\\sqrt{\\frac{\\pi}{a}}\\;e^{-2a}.\n\\]\n(In particular, for $a = 1985$ the value is $\\sqrt{\\pi/1985}\\,e^{-3970}$.)\n\nYou may assume that $\\int_{-\\infty}^\\infty e^{-x^2}\\,dx = \\sqrt{\\pi}$.\n","numLines":13,"startLine":1,"totalLines":13}}}
